# Step 1: Backup your repository\nsvnadmin dump /path/to/repository > repository-backup.dump\n\n# Step 2: Install the new version of the Subversion server\n# This process will vary depending on your operating system and package manager.\n# For example, on a Debian-based system, you might use:\nsudo apt-get update\nsudo apt-get install subversion\n\n# Step 3: Upgrade the repository format\nsvnadmin upgrade /path/to/repository\n\n# Step 4: Verify the upgrade\nsvnlook youngest /path/to/repository